# isEnabled

**Instance Property**

A Boolean value that indicates if the item is enabled.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor var isEnabled: Bool { get set }
```

## Discussion

The default value is [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/true].

## Managing Configuration

- **handler**: An optional closure that CarPlay invokes when the user selects the list item.
- **userInfo**: An opaque value for the list item.
